{"tid":2248944,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"新一代Oculus quest 2 玩Steam VR 集中討論 (6) 收到機既人表示VR係魔鬼!","createTime":"2020-10-19T04:03:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-19T05:04:14.000Z","uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"482a8de784af6c64416ef9e59116a44d3ef3f4db","tid":2248944,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T04:03:45.000Z","msg":"<p class=\"center\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">注意！避免陽光直射鏡片 會壞 玩完搵陰暗位放好佢</span></span></p><br />\n<br />\nOculus quest 2官網資料 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.oculus.com/quest-2/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.oculus.com%2Fquest-2%2F&d=89HDPkshzIuckIexGTa1ayHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=12ebe216\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.oculus.com/quest-2/</a><br />\n<br />\n美森訂購 免運費直送香港 $2362 HKD<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Oculus-Quest-Advanced-All-One-2/dp/B08F7PTF53/ref=sr_1_1_sspa?dchild=1&amp;keywords=Oculus&amp;qid=1600433942&amp;sr=8-1-spons&amp;psc=1&amp;spLa=ZW5jcnlwdGVkUXVhbGlmaWVyPUE3VElLTjNPMFBMRFgmZW5jcnlwdGVkSWQ9QTA2MDgzMjJHWUxTNERQNElRM0ImZW5jcnlwdGVkQWRJZD1BMDQ3OTg0NjhKNVc0TUxBWDdLVSZ3aWRnZXROYW1lPXNwX2F0ZiZhY3Rpb249Y2xpY2tSZWRpcmVjdCZkb05vdExvZ0NsaWNrPXRydWU=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FOculus-Quest-Advanced-All-One-2%2Fdp%2FB08F7PTF53%2Fref%3Dsr_1_1_sspa%3Fdchild%3D1%26keywords%3DOculus%26qid%3D1600433942%26sr%3D8-1-spons%26psc%3D1%26spLa%3DZW5jcnlwdGVkUXVhbGlmaWVyPUE3VElLTjNPMFBMRFgmZW5jcnlwdGVkSWQ9QTA2MDgzMjJHWUxTNERQNElRM0ImZW5jcnlwdGVkQWRJZD1BMDQ3OTg0NjhKNVc0TUxBWDdLVSZ3aWRnZXROYW1lPXNwX2F0ZiZhY3Rpb249Y2xpY2tSZWRpcmVjdCZkb05vdExvZ0NsaWNrPXRydWU%3D&d=89HDPkshzIuckIexGTa1ayHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=188c8074\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.amazon.com/Oculus-Quest-Advanced-All-One-2/dp/B08F7PTF53/ref=sr_1_1_sspa?dchild=1&amp;keywords=Oculus&amp;qid=1600433942&amp;sr=8-1-spons&amp;psc=1&amp;spLa=ZW5jcnlwdGVkUXVhbGlmaWVyPUE3VElLTjNPMFBMRFgmZW5jcnlwdGVkSWQ9QTA2MDgzMjJHWUxTNERQNElRM0ImZW5jcnlwdGVkQWRJZD1BMDQ3OTg0NjhKNVc0TUxBWDdLVSZ3aWRnZXROYW1lPXNwX2F0ZiZhY3Rpb249Y2xpY2tSZWRpcmVjdCZkb05vdExvZ0NsaWNrPXRydWU=</a><br />\n<br />\nOculus quest 2解像度比較 (目前最抵玩VR Headset)<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https://na.cx/i/PtV7Ad6.jpg&amp;h=e9ba2ee8&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n<br />\n你部電腦夠唔夠力RUN VR? 用<span class=\"red\">SteamVR PerformanceTest</span>下面可以CHECK<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://store.steampowered.com/app/323910/SteamVR_Performance_Test/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstore.steampowered.com%2Fapp%2F323910%2FSteamVR_Performance_Test%2F&d=89HDPkshzIuckIexGTa1ayHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=2801eb6c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://store.steampowered.com/app/323910/SteamVR_Performance_Test/</a><br />\n<br />\n1.咩係Oculus Quest 2? 有咩玩? 有分64GB同256GB? <br />\nOculus quest 2好似你而家用緊果部電話咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/pussy2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可以拎出街玩 唔洗額外感應器/鏡頭之類 佢本身係行ANDROID系統 有自己既遊戲平台畀人買Game玩 <br />\n<br />\n官方平台Oculus Store <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.oculus.com/experiences/quest/?locale=zh_HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.oculus.com%2Fexperiences%2Fquest%2F%3Flocale%3Dzh_HK&d=89HDPkshzIuckIexGTa1ayHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=5fa9cb12\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.oculus.com/experiences/quest/?locale=zh_HK</a><br />\n<span class=\"red\"> 有其他分類 Rift ,Go, Gear VR果D唔洗理</span> <br />\n自己睇Game list 平均一隻大約幾大容量 再決定買64GB定256GB<br />\n<br />\n亦都有第三方平台SideQuest 畀人裝Game 比較多獨立廠出Game<br />\n<a href=\"https://sidequestvr.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsidequestvr.com%2F&d=89HDPkshzIuckIexGTa1ayHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=8aeee95c\" target=\"_blank\">https://sidequestvr.com/</a><br />\n<br />\nOculus Rift Store又係咩黎?<br />\n同Steam VR一樣 要電腦去RUN  大部份VR GAMES都有Rift版同Steam VR版 <br />\n亦有獨家作品係自己平台 睇你想玩咩<br />\n<br />\n同一隻VR Game可以分為Oculus版,Rift版同Steam VR版呢三種 前者唔洗電腦好似手機Game咁但畫面會降左級,後者兩個Rift版同Steam VR要電腦 畫面最好<br />\n<br />\n2.如果只係想玩Steam VR 容量幾多好?<br />\n唔關事<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />買64GB夠用 因為Steam VR要PC去玩 部Oculus Quest 2容量幾多完全唔關事<br />\n<br />\n3.PC VR即係咩 <br />\n即係PC囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />電腦一部<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Display card要求比較高 上面有Link可以Test<br />\n<br />\n4.Steam VR有咩game 幾錢? 硬件要求高唔高?<br />\n<a href=\"https://store.steampowered.com/vr/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstore.steampowered.com%2Fvr%2F&d=89HDPkshzIuckIexGTa1ayHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=83ff85b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://store.steampowered.com/vr/</a> <br />\n自己睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n5.Steam game好貴!<br />\n去allkey睇睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.allkeyshop.com/blog/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.allkeyshop.com%2Fblog%2F&d=89HDPkshzIuckIexGTa1ayHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=d96d1775\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.allkeyshop.com/blog/</a> <br />\n<br />\n6.想玩Steam VR 除左Oculus quest 2之外 仲有咩要買? <br />\n<span class=\"red\">買VD 即係Virtual desktop 可以幫你Wireless 即係Wifi既方式連去電腦玩Steam VR 必買! <br />\nVirtual Desktop $19.99美元 一定要係Oculus Store買 唔好買錯!</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.oculus.com/experiences/quest/2017050365004772/?locale=zh_HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.oculus.com%2Fexperiences%2Fquest%2F2017050365004772%2F%3Flocale%3Dzh_HK&d=89HDPkshzIuckIexGTa1ayHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=a990ea7b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.oculus.com/experiences/quest/2017050365004772/?locale=zh_HK</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">Oculus 日後會出官方版Virtual desktop 叫Oculus Air Link 一樣都係Wireless方式連去電腦 <br />\n但係仲未出</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n玩Steam VR有兩種 插Usb線 OR Wifi連PC去玩 <br />\n<br />\n前者下載Oculus link<br />\n<a href=\"https://support.oculus.com/525406631321134/#setup\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsupport.oculus.com%2F525406631321134%2F%23setup&d=89HDPkshzIuckIexGTa1ayHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=fa670212\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://support.oculus.com/525406631321134/#setup</a><br />\n(如果Router好慢...又想玩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />是但街買Usb3.0線都得 唔洗買官方Usb線)<br />\n<br />\n後者要用Virtual desktop<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.vrdesktop.net/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vrdesktop.net%2F&d=89HDPkshzIuckIexGTa1ayHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=dda7728e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.vrdesktop.net/</a><br />\n(Oculus quest 2用Wifi連PC方法有兩種)<br />\n<br />\n1.經Router Oculus quest 2連去PC<br />\n<br />\n2.PC用Hotpot直連Oculus quest 2<br />\n<br />\n方法1 要求Router Wifi 6 5g速度with 160mhz  <br />\n當中160mhz以Wireless方式玩VR係十分重要 因為latency可以壓到最低<br />\n<br />\n方法2 AX200 5g速度with 160mhz 既Pcie wifi卡 <br />\n原因同上<br />\n<br />\nPcie wifi卡比較平 $5XX左右有得買 而Router Wifi 6 有埋160mhz 就貴d 價錢自己考慮<br />\n<br />\n如果以方法2玩VR 留意你電腦底板夠唔夠位裝Pcie wifi卡 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌msi老母 邊個設計將pcie位放到顯示卡插槽 咁撚近？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2244831/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2244831/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n以上我就係例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/handup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我係裝唔到Pcie wifi卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />強烈意見用VD 遊戲體驗係最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nOculus quest 2暫不支援160mhz 最多80Mhz<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Quest 2粒CPU XR2硬件上係支援到160mhz <br />\n可惜被Fackbook封印左<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而家買唔買160mhz 自己考慮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n感謝Game長文解釋160MHZ重要性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n[VR撚] Oculus Quest 2 Link vs Wifi5 VD vs Wifi6 VD<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2240879/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2240879/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nFAQ 感謝Gamel提供<br />\n1.) 應唔應該加錢買elite頭帶？<br />\n有review話都係DAS舒服啲，姐係halo strap會更舒服(唔係每個人既頭都適合halo strap)，想試好簡單，去試PSVR，你覺得舒服就証明halo strap岩你頭型。不過如果你覺得PSVR唔舒服既，記得加錢買elite頭帶，我推薦有埋電池既elite頭帶，因為DAS都要加電池做balance先真正舒服，elite同design同理，不過記得唔好扔原廠頭帶，訓平睇戲果陣會舒服好多，無野頂住<br />\n<br />\n感謝gamel 提供詳細VD設定教學<br />\nVD設定連線去PC 過程會比較繁複<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/darkness.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/presentation/d/1VlDuogD7LN_wzdPfkNn6OqcNrqAmBdkxmYDG9mcZBsM/edit?usp=drivesdk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fpresentation%2Fd%2F1VlDuogD7LN_wzdPfkNn6OqcNrqAmBdkxmYDG9mcZBsM%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Ddrivesdk&d=89HDPkshzIuckIexGTa1ayHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=63abe951\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/presentation/d/1VlDuogD7LN_wzdPfkNn6OqcNrqAmBdkxmYDG9mcZBsM/edit?usp=drivesdk</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">注意！避免陽光直射鏡片 會壞 玩完搵陰暗位放好佢</span></span></p>"},{"pid":"f06ea9a3c5915bd87fce9f52eb619fa433587fcb","tid":2248944,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T04:04:13.000Z","msg":"DEMO入門APPS推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://sidebookvr.files.wordpress.com/2020/10/101a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsidebookvr.files.wordpress.com%2F2020%2F10%2F101a.jpg&h=5fe5806f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nFirst Steps for Quest 2<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ocu